title: Beads Math
description: Mobile application to improve maths calculation skills.

body.raw: What is abacus? An abacus is a method of calculation that has been used for centuries before the advent of calculators. Types of abacus There are many types of abacus. The type of abacus that will be used now is the Japanese abacus. Using abacus as a base, it is a method of simultaneously teaching mental arithmetic. Benefits - Brain Development - Improve in Math Skills (Beads Maths application can be used not only for abacus math calculations but also for other math calculations.) Contact Phone or Viber: +959256199989 Mail: kidsbrainwork2022@gmail.com
